30:38.125 --> 30:40.541
<i>Dang,
if I was gonna learn anything here,</i>

30:40.541 --> 30:41.833
<i>it was gonna be from this guy.</i>

30:41.833 --> 30:44.916
<i>But he was shut up tighter
