Hey, Clarence, some of these chips
are looking overcooked.

31:51.750 --> 31:53.083
Should the heat be adjusted?

31:53.958 --> 31:57.000
Nah, brown ones
are separated and then tossed.

31:58.583 --> 31:59.833
