31:59.833 --> 32:01.250
Dang.

32:02.708 --> 32:04.791
People always trying
to throw away the brown ones.

32:08.958 --> 32:11.541
Montañez, you missed a spot.

32:12.625 --> 32:14.125
Watch yourself, Carson.

32:15.416 --> 32:17.375
I'm always missin' a spot.

32:19.541 --> 32:20.541
Hey.

32:21.250 --> 32:22.625
Leave it.

32:23.625 --> 32:24.875
Come with me.

32:25.666 --> 32:26.708
Stand right there...

32:29.250 --> 32:30.458
...and listen.

32:38.416 --> 32:40.375
Gasket's loose in station seven.

32:42.958 --> 32:45.000
That's all I got to do, is listen.

32:45.583 --> 32:51.250
I can tell you which machine,
belt, drum, valve or motor that's off.

32:51.250 --> 32:55.083
