33:04.166 --> 33:06.583
Oh, you will when I'm done with you.

33:08.416 --> 33:10.458
You ain't a nobody, son.

33:15.791 --> 33:16.791
<i>Heck yeah.</i>

33:16.791 --> 33:18.833
<i>I was officially his protégé.</i>

33:19.541 --> 33:22.875
<i>But I had to learn it on my own time,
