<i>of the federal government.</i>

34:24.291 --> 34:26.708
<i>Man,
these Reagan years weren't kind to nobody.</i>

34:26.708 --> 34:27.791
1985

34:27.791 --> 34:30.041
<i>Nothing trickling down
to the</i> pobres <i>and</i> prietos <i>like us.</i>

34:30.041 --> 34:32.791
<i>Deep cuts are planned
for programs designed for the poor...</i>

