41:29.458 --> 41:30.791
-<i>...we should get our...</i>

41:37.583 --> 41:38.958
-  <i>Papi!</i>
-  Can't wait.

41:38.958 --> 41:40.083
Hey!

41:40.083 --> 41:42.166
How was your day?

41:42.166 --> 41:43.250
- Good.
