Hey! What's the matter with you?

42:00.833 --> 42:06.541
Don't look at me. I love <i>elote</i>.
I love beans. I love rice. I love tamales.

42:06.541 --> 42:09.875
He's just mad 'cause kids make fun of him
'cause we're Mexican.

42:09.875 --> 42:11.333
- Man, shut up!
- Hey, you shut up!

42:11.333 --> 42:12.916
- Hey! Knock it off.
- Hey!

42:12.916 --> 42:13.833
Stop.

42:17.041 --> 42:18.041
Is that true?

42:19.666 --> 42:21.541
Are some little pricks picking on you?

