Sure, sure. Uh, Richard!

01:08:40.708 --> 01:08:41.791
I'm here!

01:08:59.791 --> 01:09:02.375
The infamous Richard Montañez.

01:09:02.375 --> 01:09:04.375
What an honor to meet you, Richard.

01:09:04.375 --> 01:09:05.625
Are you ready?

01:09:05.625 --> 01:09:07.916
<i>A huevo.</i> I've been ready.

01:09:07.916 --> 01:09:09.125
