01:23:54.583 --> 01:23:57.125
<i>And then Enrico went OG on 'em.</i>

01:23:57.125 --> 01:24:00.083
<i>"You ain't never
gonna eat another Cheeto in your life.</i>

01:24:00.583 --> 01:24:02.041
<i>You dig,</i> carnal<i>?"</i>

01:24:03.750 --> 01:24:05.791
<i>Nah, I'm just playin'.
It didn't go down like that.</i>

01:24:05.791 --> 01:24:08.375
<i>You think these fools had that in them?</i>
Chale.

01:24:08.375 --> 01:24:11.833
Here's the latest sales report
on Flamin' Hot Cheetos.

01:24:13.875 --> 01:24:16.333
Whoa, Finley.
