01:25:09.833 --> 01:25:12.250
<i>Richard? It's Roger Enrico.</i>

01:25:13.541 --> 01:25:14.750
Hello, sir.

01:25:14.750 --> 01:25:16.541
<i>We're gonna need more cases.</i>

01:25:17.666 --> 01:25:19.333
Oh-- Yeah-- Okay.

01:25:19.333 --> 01:25:21.375
